 <h2>Snake Pit in Blackburrow</h2><br><br><br>In BlackBurrow, there is a ledge with some snakes, and it can be fairly decent experience.<br><br>You can go there any level from 8 onwards, but at level8 you should really be duoing at the least, when you get a little higher it can be very good solo experience.<br><br>Its almost train-free (for Blackburrow this is amazing!), the exp is good, and you wont require a big group all the time like other camps.<br><br><br><br></center><b><u>Zone Information:</u></b><br><br><a href='http://www.eqmages.com' onClick='moblist(18); return false;'>Blackburrow mob list</a><br>
